page.title: 20ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS,L/CATSHILL
page.content:
This disc was prepared by all the children in the fourth year of Lickey First and Middle School, Rednal, near Birmingham,under the guidance of Miss J.Wilson and Mr C.Morris. Mr A.Kettle acted as computer consultant. The information could not have been collected without the kind help of many people living and working in the Lickey and Catshill area. We would like to extend our grateful thanks to everyone including especially those responsible for the following places to which visits were made:
Bromsgrove Police Station Cofton Post_Natal Clinic Bromsgrove Job Centre Hazel Robinson (hairdressers) Hair Flair (hairdressers) Lower Shepley Farm Douglas Construction Site,Alvechurch.
